  "root_text": {
    "snp1.6:0.1": "Sutta Nipāta 1.6 ",
    "snp1.6:0.2": "Parābhavasutta ",
    "snp1.6:1.1": "Evaṁ me sutaṁ—",
    "snp1.6:1.2": "ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṁ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
    "snp1.6:1.3": "Atha kho aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṁ jetavanaṁ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṁ abhivādetvā ekamantaṁ aṭṭhāsi. ",
    "snp1.6:1.4": "Ekamantaṁ ṭhitā kho sā devatā bhagavantaṁ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
    "snp1.6:2.1": "“Parābhavantaṁ purisaṁ, ",
    "snp1.6:2.2": "mayaṁ pucchāma gotama; ",
    "snp1.6:2.3": "Bhavantaṁ puṭṭhumāgamma, ",
    "snp1.6:2.4": "kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:3.1": "“Suvijāno bhavaṁ hoti, ",
    "snp1.6:3.2": "suvijāno parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:3.3": "Dhammakāmo bhavaṁ hoti, ",
    "snp1.6:3.4": "dhammadessī parābhavo”. ",
    "snp1.6:4.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:4.2": "paṭhamo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:4.3": "Dutiyaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:4.4": "kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:5.1": "“Asantassa piyā honti, ",
    "snp1.6:5.2": "sante na kurute piyaṁ; ",
    "snp1.6:5.3": "Asataṁ dhammaṁ roceti, ",
    "snp1.6:5.4": "taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:6.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:6.2": "dutiyo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:6.3": "Tatiyaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:6.4": "kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:7.1": "“Niddāsīlī sabhāsīlī, ",
    "snp1.6:7.2": "anuṭṭhātā ca yo naro; ",
    "snp1.6:7.3": "Alaso kodhapaññāṇo, ",
    "snp1.6:7.4": "taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:8.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:8.2": "tatiyo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:8.3": "Catutthaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:8.4": "kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:9.1": "“Yo mātaraṁ pitaraṁ vā, ",
    "snp1.6:9.2": "jiṇṇakaṁ gatayobbanaṁ; ",
    "snp1.6:9.3": "Pahu santo na bharati, ",
    "snp1.6:9.4": "taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:10.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:10.2": "catuttho so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:10.3": "Pañcamaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:10.4": "kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:11.1": "“Yo brāhmaṇaṁ samaṇaṁ vā, ",
    "snp1.6:11.2": "Aññaṁ vāpi vanibbakaṁ; ",
    "snp1.6:11.3": "Musāvādena vañceti, ",
    "snp1.6:11.4": "Taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:12.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:12.2": "Pañcamo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:12.3": "Chaṭṭhamaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:12.4": "Kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:13.1": "“Pahūtavitto puriso, ",
    "snp1.6:13.2": "Sahirañño sabhojano; ",
    "snp1.6:13.3": "Eko bhuñjati sādūni, ",
    "snp1.6:13.4": "Taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:14.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:14.2": "Chaṭṭhamo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:14.3": "Sattamaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:14.4": "Kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:15.1": "“Jātitthaddho dhanatthaddho, ",
    "snp1.6:15.2": "Gottatthaddho ca yo naro; ",
    "snp1.6:15.3": "Saññātiṁ atimaññeti, ",
    "snp1.6:15.4": "Taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:16.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:16.2": "Sattamo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:16.3": "Aṭṭhamaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:16.4": "Kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:17.1": "“Itthidhutto surādhutto, ",
    "snp1.6:17.2": "Akkhadhutto ca yo naro; ",
    "snp1.6:17.3": "Laddhaṁ laddhaṁ vināseti, ",
    "snp1.6:17.4": "Taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:18.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:18.2": "Aṭṭhamo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:18.3": "Navamaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:18.4": "Kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:19.1": "“Sehi dārehi asantuṭṭho, ",
    "snp1.6:19.2": "Vesiyāsu padussati; ",
    "snp1.6:19.3": "Dussati paradāresu, ",
    "snp1.6:19.4": "Taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:20.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:20.2": "Navamo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:20.3": "Dasamaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:20.4": "Kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:21.1": "“Atītayobbano poso, ",
    "snp1.6:21.2": "Āneti timbarutthaniṁ; ",
    "snp1.6:21.3": "Tassā issā na supati, ",
    "snp1.6:21.4": "Taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:22.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:22.2": "Dasamo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:22.3": "Ekādasamaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:22.4": "Kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:23.1": "“Itthiṁ soṇḍiṁ vikiraṇiṁ, ",
    "snp1.6:23.2": "Purisaṁ vāpi tādisaṁ; ",
    "snp1.6:23.3": "Issariyasmiṁ ṭhapeti, ",
    "snp1.6:23.4": "Taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:24.1": "“Iti hetaṁ vijānāma, ",
    "snp1.6:24.2": "Ekādasamo so parābhavo; ",
    "snp1.6:24.3": "Dvādasamaṁ bhagavā brūhi, ",
    "snp1.6:24.4": "Kiṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ”. ",
    "snp1.6:25.1": "“Appabhogo mahātaṇho, ",
    "snp1.6:25.2": "Khattiye jāyate kule; ",
    "snp1.6:25.3": "So ca rajjaṁ patthayati, ",
    "snp1.6:25.4": "Taṁ parābhavato mukhaṁ. ",
    "snp1.6:26.1": "Ete parābhave loke, ",
    "snp1.6:26.2": "Paṇḍito samavekkhiya; ",
    "snp1.6:26.3": "Ariyo dassanasampanno, ",
    "snp1.6:26.4": "Sa lokaṁ bhajate sivan”ti. ",
    "snp1.6:26.5": "Parābhavasuttaṁ chaṭṭhaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "snp1.6:0.1": "Anthology of Discourses 1.6 ",
    "snp1.6:0.2": "Downfalls ",
    "snp1.6:1.1": "So I have heard. ",
    "snp1.6:1.2": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. ",
    "snp1.6:1.3": "Then, late at night, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, and stood to one side. ",
    "snp1.6:1.4": "Standing to one side, that deity addressed the Buddha in verse: ",
    "snp1.6:2.1": "“We ask Gotama ",
    "snp1.6:2.2": "about a man’s downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:2.3": "We have come to ask you, sir: ",
    "snp1.6:2.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:3.1": "“It’s easy to understand success, ",
    "snp1.6:3.2": "understanding downfall is just as easy. ",
    "snp1.6:3.3": "One who loves the teaching succeeds, ",
    "snp1.6:3.4": "but a hater of the teaching meets their downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:4.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:4.2": "this is the first downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:4.3": "Tell us the second, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:4.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:5.1": "“The bad are dear to him, ",
    "snp1.6:5.2": "he has no love for the good. ",
    "snp1.6:5.3": "He believes the teaching of the bad; ",
    "snp1.6:5.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:6.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:6.2": "this is the second downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:6.3": "Tell us the third, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:6.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:7.1": "“Fond of sleep, fond of company, ",
    "snp1.6:7.2": "a man who does no work; ",
    "snp1.6:7.3": "he’s lazy, marked by anger, ",
    "snp1.6:7.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:8.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:8.2": "this is the third downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:8.3": "Tell us the fourth, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:8.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:9.1": "“Though able, he does not look after ",
    "snp1.6:9.2": "his mother and father ",
    "snp1.6:9.3": "when elderly, past their prime, ",
    "snp1.6:9.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:10.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:10.2": "this is the fourth downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:10.3": "Tell us the fifth, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:10.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:11.1": "“He deceives with lies ",
    "snp1.6:11.2": "ascetics and brahmins ",
    "snp1.6:11.3": "and other supplicants, ",
    "snp1.6:11.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:12.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:12.2": "this is the fifth downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:12.3": "Tell us the sixth, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:12.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:13.1": "“A man with plenty of wealth, ",
    "snp1.6:13.2": "including gold coin and food, ",
    "snp1.6:13.3": "eats delicacies alone, ",
    "snp1.6:13.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:14.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:14.2": "this is the sixth downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:14.3": "Tell us the seventh, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:14.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:15.1": "“Vain of birth, wealth, ",
    "snp1.6:15.2": "and clan, a man ",
    "snp1.6:15.3": "looks down on his own family, ",
    "snp1.6:15.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:16.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:16.2": "this is the seventh downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:16.3": "Tell us the eighth, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:16.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:17.1": "“In womanizing, drinking, ",
    "snp1.6:17.2": "and gambling, a man ",
    "snp1.6:17.3": "wastes all that he has earned, ",
    "snp1.6:17.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:18.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:18.2": "this is the eighth downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:18.3": "Tell us the ninth, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:18.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:19.1": "“Not content with his own partners, ",
    "snp1.6:19.2": "he debauches himself with prostitutes, ",
    "snp1.6:19.3": "and with others’ partners, ",
    "snp1.6:19.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:20.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:20.2": "this is the ninth downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:20.3": "Tell us the tenth, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:20.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:21.1": "“A man well past his prime ",
    "snp1.6:21.2": "marries a girl with budding breasts; ",
    "snp1.6:21.3": "he cannot sleep for jealousy, ",
    "snp1.6:21.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:22.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:22.2": "this is the tenth downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:22.3": "Tell us the eleventh, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:22.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:23.1": "“He places in authority ",
    "snp1.6:23.2": "a woman or a man ",
    "snp1.6:23.3": "who’s a drunkard and a wastrel, ",
    "snp1.6:23.4": "and that leads to his downfall.” ",
    "snp1.6:24.1": "“We understand what you’re saying, ",
    "snp1.6:24.2": "this is the eleventh downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:24.3": "Tell us the twelfth, Blessed One: ",
    "snp1.6:24.4": "what leads to downfall?” ",
    "snp1.6:25.1": "“A man of little wealth and strong craving, ",
    "snp1.6:25.2": "born into an aristocratic family, ",
    "snp1.6:25.3": "sets his sights on kingship, ",
    "snp1.6:25.4": "and that leads to his downfall. ",
    "snp1.6:26.1": "Seeing these downfalls in the world, ",
    "snp1.6:26.2": "an astute and noble person, ",
    "snp1.6:26.3": "accomplished in vision, ",
    "snp1.6:26.4": "will enjoy a world of grace.” "
  },
